  "text": "—email— Hi FrankI see you posted my secret last week. But you only showed the side that said to put it in the freezer. That wasn’t the secret! The secret itself was on the other side. It would appear when you freeze the postcard.-M—email—Hi M,Your postcard has had an interesting journey in my home. My wife has discovered postcards all over our house but never in our freezer! When she asked me about it, I told her it was written with cold-sensitive ink, and I put it there in hopes of revealing its secret. It worked! But when I set it aside for a few days, the ink disappeared and wouldn’t return, even when I refroze it. Do you remember the secret?-F —email—Oh, no!Sure, the double haiku is burned into my brain:Fired my therapist‘Cos I had a crush on himHe confessed the sameI am married. WeLive on different continentsIt could never work.—email—Hey Frank,What is the weirdest thing you have signed at a PostSecret event? —email—Hi Frank,I have been a fan of PostSecret since I first heard about it. I am an animator and illustrator and over the past few months I was struggling to find inspiration for a personal project. Then I had the idea of turning some secrets into little vignettes and stringing them together to make a longer video. I thoroughly enjoyed making this animation and I hope you like it too!! https://vimeo.com/1062509027 —email—Dear Frank, Last year I sent in my secret about struggling to forgive my mom and Eddie Vedder showing me how. You posted it in November. On December 22, 2024 my mom was diagnosed with cancer of the brain. She passed away on February 18, 2025. I was with her during her last week of life. I told her I loved her. I told her I forgive her and I asked her to forgive me. I was with her when she drew her last breath. The power of forgiveness is freeing. I encourage anyone who is lucky enough to have a living parent to call them right away. Have the difficult conversations. Do it before it’s too late. And if the conversation is just too damn difficult… then just say “Thank you. I love you and I forgive you. Please forgive me.”Peace,M.B.",
  "image": "https://postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/freezer-526x351.jpg",
  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"page\" role=\"main\"\u003e\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\u003carticle id=\"post-48355\"\u003e\n    \n\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"526\" height=\"351\" data-attachment-id=\"48146\" data-permalink=\"https://postsecret.com/?attachment_id=48146#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/freezer.jpg?fit=708%2C472\u0026amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"708,472\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;Perfection V600\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;1\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"freezer\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/freezer.jpg?fit=300%2C200\u0026amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/freezer.jpg?fit=526%2C351\u0026amp;ssl=1\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/freezer.jpg?resize=526%2C351\u0026amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/freezer.jpg?resize=526%2C351\u0026amp;ssl=1 526w, https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/freezer.jpg?resize=300%2C200\u0026amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/freezer.jpg?resize=150%2C100\u0026amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/freezer.jpg?w=708\u0026amp;ssl=1 708w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 526px) 100vw, 526px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e—email— \u003cbr/\u003eHi Frank\u003cbr/\u003eI see you posted my secret last week. But you only showed the side that said to put it in the freezer. That wasn’t the secret! The secret itself was on the other side. It would appear when you freeze the postcard.\u003cbr/\u003e-M\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e—email—\u003cbr/\u003eHi M,\u003cbr/\u003eYour postcard has had an interesting journey in my home. My wife has discovered postcards all over our house but never in our freezer! When she asked me about it, I told her it was written with cold-sensitive ink, and I put it there in hopes of revealing its secret. It worked! But when I set it aside for a few days, the ink disappeared and wouldn’t return, even when I refroze it. Do you remember the secret?\u003cbr/\u003e-F\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e—email—\u003cbr/\u003eOh, no!\u003cbr/\u003eSure, the double haiku is burned into my brain:\u003cbr/\u003eFired my therapist\u003cbr/\u003e‘Cos I had a crush on him\u003cbr/\u003eHe confessed the same\u003cbr/\u003eI am married. We\u003cbr/\u003eLive on different continents\u003cbr/\u003eIt could never work.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e—email—\u003cbr/\u003eHey Frank,\u003cbr/\u003eWhat is the weirdest thing you have signed at a PostSecret event?\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"526\" height=\"351\" data-attachment-id=\"48364\" data-permalink=\"https://postsecret.com/2025/03/30/frankpostsecret-com/skull-3/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/skull.jpg?fit=900%2C600\u0026amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"900,600\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;5\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;Canon EOS REBEL T3i\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;1329430179\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;45\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;3200\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0.076923076923077\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;1\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"skull\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/skull.jpg?fit=300%2C200\u0026amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/skull.jpg?fit=526%2C351\u0026amp;ssl=1\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/skull.jpg?resize=526%2C351\u0026amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/skull.jpg?resize=526%2C351\u0026amp;ssl=1 526w, https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/skull.jpg?resize=300%2C200\u0026amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/skull.jpg?resize=150%2C100\u0026amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/skull.jpg?resize=768%2C512\u0026amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/skull.jpg?w=900\u0026amp;ssl=1 900w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 526px) 100vw, 526px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e—email—\u003cbr/\u003eHi Frank,\u003cbr/\u003eI have been a fan of PostSecret since I first heard about it. I am an animator and illustrator and over the past few months I was struggling to find inspiration for a personal project. Then I had the idea of turning some secrets into little vignettes and stringing them together to make a longer video. I thoroughly enjoyed making this animation and I hope you like it too!! \u003ca href=\"https://vimeo.com/1062509027\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003ehttps://vimeo.com/1062509027\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"526\" height=\"312\" data-attachment-id=\"48362\" data-permalink=\"https://postsecret.com/2025/03/30/frankpostsecret-com/screen-shot-2025-03-29-at-7-01-35-pm/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Screen-Shot-2025-03-29-at-7.01.35-PM.png?fit=960%2C569\u0026amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"960,569\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"Screen Shot 2025-03-29 at 7.01.35 PM\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Screen-Shot-2025-03-29-at-7.01.35-PM.png?fit=300%2C178\u0026amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Screen-Shot-2025-03-29-at-7.01.35-PM.png?fit=526%2C312\u0026amp;ssl=1\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Screen-Shot-2025-03-29-at-7.01.35-PM.png?resize=526%2C312\u0026amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Screen-Shot-2025-03-29-at-7.01.35-PM.png?resize=526%2C312\u0026amp;ssl=1 526w, https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Screen-Shot-2025-03-29-at-7.01.35-PM.png?resize=300%2C178\u0026amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Screen-Shot-2025-03-29-at-7.01.35-PM.png?resize=150%2C89\u0026amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Screen-Shot-2025-03-29-at-7.01.35-PM.png?resize=768%2C455\u0026amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Screen-Shot-2025-03-29-at-7.01.35-PM.png?w=960\u0026amp;ssl=1 960w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 526px) 100vw, 526px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e—email—\u003cbr/\u003eDear Frank, \u003cbr/\u003eLast year I sent in my secret about struggling to forgive my mom and Eddie Vedder showing me how. You posted it in November. On December 22, 2024 my mom was diagnosed with cancer of the brain. She passed away on February 18, 2025. I was with her during her last week of life. I told her I loved her. I told her I forgive her and I asked her to forgive me. I was with her when she drew her last breath. The power of forgiveness is freeing. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eI encourage anyone who is lucky enough to have a living parent to call them right away. Have the difficult conversations. Do it before it’s too late. And if the conversation is just too damn difficult… then just say “Thank you. I love you and I forgive you. Please forgive me.”\u003cbr/\u003ePeace,\u003cbr/\u003eM.B.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"526\" height=\"312\" data-attachment-id=\"48366\" data-permalink=\"https://postsecret.com/2025/03/30/frankpostsecret-com/eddie-2/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/postsecret.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/eddie.jpg?fit=812%2C481\u0026amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"812,481\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0